column2: You dumb fucking cretin, you fucking fool, absolute fucking buffoon, you bumbling idiot. Fuck you.

You either come to Brazil or Brazil will come for you.
Why don't we come to Brazil.
Bro did you just abandon your religion? That's cringe ngl.

A Confucian teaching that instructs people to eat until they are 80 percent full, which only got popular in Ryukyu and made the Ryukyuans have the highest life expectancy worldwide for centuries.
We can't really call ourselves Scottish if we don't use Scottish names of our lands.
The invaders are gone, let us return to the old ways and our own language.
Why have readable province names when we can just use our unintelligible language. They can't formally declare war on us if they can't spell our name. Like there's 11 ways to say "Welsh" in Welsh.
The Order of the Dragon was a monarchical chivalric order for originally catholic knights and monarchs to fight the enemies of christianity.
Revive the Order of the Dragon
It is time once again to reestablish the long gone order to fight off the infidels. Awaken the dragon of the Balkan!
After the Kalmyks settled, all remaining local Tatars became vassals of the Oirats. Now that Astrakhan became independent, let us maintain this formality, together we are stronger.
